headline: Is There Opportunity in Nasdaq After Its Push Into Data and Analytics Services?
summary: Thinking about what to do with your Nasdaq shares, or eyeing them for your portfolio? You’re not alone in weighing your options. The stock’s trajectory in recent months has left investors curious, and maybe a bit excited. Despite a very slight dip over the past week, Nasdaq’s share price is up 1.5% for the past month and it has stacked up some seriously impressive returns: 14.2% year-to-date and nearly 20% over the past year. Zoom out even further, and that five-year gain of almost 135%...
